smartnode.name: smartnode

smartnode.description: The MIB module to describe the system specific parameters of a SmartNode.

serialNumber.name: serialNumber
serialNumber.description: Provides the serial number of the device.

hwRelease.name: hwRelease
hwRelease.description: Provides the hardware release of the device.

hwVersion.name: hwVersion
hwVersion.description: Provides the hardware version of the device.

swVersion.name: swVersion
swVersion.description: Provides the software version of the device. The following is an example of a software version information: R4.2 2008-09-11 SIP

productName.name: productName
productName.description: Provides the product name of the device.

dslSwVersion.name: dslSwVersion
dslSwVersion.description: Provides the firmware version of the DSL card if any present

uploadExecute.name: uploadExecute
uploadExecute.description: Starts configuration upload via TFTP. 0 noOp 1 uploadConfiguration

uploadTftpServerPath.name: uploadTftpServerPath
uploadTftpServerPath.description: Server path and file name on which the configuration will be stored. ( e.g. configurations/config1.cfg )

uploadStatus.name: uploadStatus
uploadStatus.description: The status of the running configuration transfer from the device to a file on the TFTP server. 0 failed 1 success 2 inProgress

downloadExecute.name: downloadExecute
downloadExecute.description: Starts configuration download via TFTP. A reload of the device will be necessary in order to apply the new downloaded configuration. 0 noOP 1 downloadConfiguration

downloadTftpServerPath.name: downloadTftpServerPath
downloadTftpServerPath.description: Server path and file name from which the configuration will be downloaded ( e.g. configurations/config1.cfg ).

downloadStatus.name: downloadStatus
downloadStatus.description: The status of the configuration file transfer from the TFTP server to the device's startup configuration. 0 failed 1 success 2 inProgress

firmwareLoadExecute.name: firmwareLoadExecute
firmwareLoadExecute.description: Starts firmware download via TFTP. 0 noOp 1 loadFirmware

firmwareTftpServerPath.name: firmwareTftpServerPath
firmwareTftpServerPath.description: Server path and file name of the firmware batch-file. ( e.g. firmware/b )

firmwareLoadStatus.name: firmwareLoadStatus
firmwareLoadStatus.description: The status of the firmware download from the TFTP server to the device. 0 failed 1 success 2 inProgress

deviceReload.name: deviceReload
deviceReload.description: Force a reload of the device. 0 noOp 1 reload

saveRunningConfig.name: saveRunningConfig
saveRunningConfig.description: Save the device running configuration into the startup configuration. 0 noOp 1 saveConfiguration

cpuNumber.name: cpuNumber
cpuNumber.description: The number of CPUs present on this system.

cpuTable.name: cpuTable
cpuTable.description: A list of CPU entries. The number of entries is given by the value of cpuNumber.

cpuEntry.name: cpuEntry
cpuEntry.description: A CPU entry containing objects for corresponding to the CPU.

cpuWorkloadCurrent.name: cpuWorkloadCurrent
cpuWorkloadCurrent.description: The current CPU workload in percent.

cpuWorkload1MinuteAverage.name: cpuWorkload1MinuteAverage
cpuWorkload1MinuteAverage.description: The CPU workload average over the last minute in percent.

cpuWorkload5MinuteAverage.name: cpuWorkload5MinuteAverage
cpuWorkload5MinuteAverage.description: The CPU workload average over the last 5 minutes in percent.

memoryPoolNumber.name: memoryPoolNumber
memoryPoolNumber.description: The number of memory pools present on this system.

memoryPoolTable.name: memoryPoolTable
memoryPoolTable.description: A list of memory pool entries. The number of entries is given by the value of memoryPoolNumber.

memoryPoolEntry.name: memoryPoolEntry
memoryPoolEntry.description: A memory pool entry containing objects for the corresponding memory pool.

memDescr.name: memDescr
memDescr.description: A name identifying the memory pool.

memTotalBytes.name: memTotalBytes
memTotalBytes.description: The total number of bytes belonging to the memory pool.

memAllocatedBytes.name: memAllocatedBytes
memAllocatedBytes.description: The current number of allocated bytes in the memory pool.

memFreeBytes.name: memFreeBytes
memFreeBytes.description: The current number of free bytes in the memory pool.

memLargestFreeBlock.name: memLargestFreeBlock
memLargestFreeBlock.description: The size of the largest available free block.

memAllocatedBlocks.name: memAllocatedBlocks
memAllocatedBlocks.description: The current number of allocated blocks in the memory pool.

memFreeBlocks.name: memFreeBlocks
memFreeBlocks.description: The current number of free blocks in the memory pool.

tempProbeNumber.name: tempProbeNumber
tempProbeNumber.description: The number of temperature probes present on this system.

tempProbeTable.name: tempProbeTable
tempProbeTable.description: A list of temperature probe entries. The number of entries is given by the value of tempProbeNumber.

tempProbeEntry.name: tempProbeEntry
tempProbeEntry.description: A temperature probe entry containing objects for the corresponding temperature probe.

tempProbeDescr.name: tempProbeDescr
tempProbeDescr.description: A description for the temperature probe.

currentDegreesCelsius.name: currentDegreesCelsius
currentDegreesCelsius.description: The current temperature measured by the temperature probe in degrees celsius.

gwNumber.name: gwNumber
gwNumber.description: The number of gateways present on this system.

gwTable.name: gwTable
gwTable.description: A list of gateway entries. The number of entries is given by the value of gwNumber.

gwEntry.name: gwEntry
gwEntry.description: A gateway entry containing objects for the corresponding gateway.

gwDescr.name: gwDescr
gwDescr.description: A description of the gateway type.

gwCurrentConnectedCalls.name: gwCurrentConnectedCalls
gwCurrentConnectedCalls.description: The total number of calls on all instances of this gateway type that are currently in the connected state.

gwCurrentOngoingCalls.name: gwCurrentOngoingCalls
gwCurrentOngoingCalls.description: The total number of calls on all instances of this gateway type that are currently in the connected, a call setup or a call clearing state.

gwTotalAccumulatedCalls.name: gwTotalAccumulatedCalls
gwTotalAccumulatedCalls.description: The total accumulated number of calls processed on all instances of this gateway type since the system has started.
